hree in the bottom row. Each box represents an inch. The base of the rectan=
gle is three inches. What is that length in centimeters?</p><p><img style=
=3D"width: 100%; max-width: 261px; margin: auto;" src=3D"https://byu-pathwa=
y.brightspotcdn.com/5d/00/01b201f84af0b10ce768439f6d32/m12-02-fig03.png" al=
