he bottom row. Each box is one inch wide.">&nbsp;<br></p><p class=3D"cms-te=
xtAlign-center">Figure 1</p><p>The calculation to do this is a unit convers=
ion because you are converting from inches to an equivalent length in centi=
meters. </p><p><mjx-container class=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"=
